## Combustion Chamber Capacity Ratio

This article is dedicated to the compression ratio of [piston engines](/Reciprocating_engine). It’s crucial to distinguish this from the [overall compression ratio](/Overall_compression_ratio) found in [gas turbine](/Gas_turbine) or [jet engine](/Jet_engine) systems, which operate on entirely different thermodynamic principles. Furthermore, for those whose minds wander to digital realms, this is not to be confused with [data compression ratio](/Data_compression_ratio), a concept entirely unrelated to the mechanical realities of internal combustion.

